flowRoot.flowPara: Create a 3D video game working in web browsers
With no installation, working on phone, tablet and computer.
Three.js is a javascript library that makes WebGL - 3D in the browser - easy to use.
It provide basic shapes like cube, sphere and let you animates its.
We started with a simple scene showing a sea, we added the boat, islands...
Then we added controls, animations and interactions.
You wake up on your boat in an unknown location.
You have to find your way back home.
Along your sailing you will meet people who will help you in your journey. Maybe...
An adventure about sailing back home
